definition: abbr. for 眾議院|众议院[Zhong4 yi4 yuan4], House of Representatives
many/much/often/a lot of/numerous/more/in excess/how (to what extent)/multi-/Taiwan pr. [duo2] when it means "how"

sentences.english: These arenormally sedate affairs where empty chairs outnumber the audience.
sentences.chinese: 一般来说，空椅子比听众多是读书会上很平常的事。

sentences.english: Many spot lights towards a central point on a piece of white paper.
sentences.chinese: 众多的聚光灯都照向一张白纸的中心点。

sentences.english: The design of the car has inspired many imitations.
sentences.chinese: 这辆轿车的设计引起了众多模仿。

sentences.english: Santanas, especially the new 2000models, have become big sellers.
sentences.chinese: 桑塔纳，特别是现代2000，拥有众多的买家。

sentences.english: Hua Hong NEC's booth attracted and impressed many visitors.
sentences.chinese: 华虹NEC新颖别致的展台吸引了众多参观者。

sentences.english: Loud, persistent ringing in the ears, known as tinnitus, can be vexing for its millions of sufferers.
sentences.chinese: 耳朵里持续嘈杂的声音使众多耳鸣患者烦恼不堪。

sentences.english: Silent lamb The freshly-made lambs are sold at the commercial area with many tourists.
sentences.chinese: 《沉默的羔羊》在游人众多的商业点，羔羊现杀现卖。

sentences.english: The family that sold it to Mr. Gittes had turned it into a warren of apartments for various relatives.
sentences.chinese: 卖给吉茨的这家人把它变成了众多亲属居住的大杂院。

sentences.english: When you look at the books, you see he is just one of a hundred students or whatever.
sentences.chinese: 你看看账本就会明白他只是众多富家子弟中的一员。

sentences.english: The central area is characterized by many lakes, bogs and low ridges.
sentences.chinese: 中部的平原地带以众多的湖泊，沼泽和低岭为特点。

sentences.english: Many chemists pay attention to how to make good use of the non-active microorganism.
sentences.chinese: 如何有效合理利用这些菌株，是众多学者关注的问题。

sentences.english: Numerous uniform configurations and merchandise have brought new life to the "Golden Gaels".
sentences.chinese: 众多的统一配置和商品带来了新的生活“金盖尔人”。

sentences.english: There were many Taoist sects in the T'ang Dynasty, in which, the Shangqing Sect had the most important influence.
sentences.chinese: 在唐代众多的道教派别中，上清派的影响最大。

sentences.english: There were never more highly skilled workmen than those who lived in ancient China.
sentences.chinese: 在古代中国有着众多的手艺高超的能工巧匠。

sentences.english: What is the number of real estate tycoons Zhujiaokuai favor of a plus?
sentences.chinese: 到底是什么让众多的地产巨子对住交会青睐有加呢？

sentences.english: So the term “middle class” covers a multitude of differences.
sentences.chinese: 因此，“中产阶级”这个术语涵盖了众多的差异。
